-- Iran Ex-Guards Commander Rezai to Run in 2013 Race, ILNA Says
-- B y   L a d a n e   N a s s e r i
-- 2012-06-10T08:52:24Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-10/iran-ex-guards-commander-rezai-to-run-in-2013-race-ilna-says.html
Mohsen Rezai, the secretary of  Iran ’s
Expediency Council, announced his candidacy for next year’s
presidential election, the  Iranian Labour News Agency  reported.  “My presence in the next presidential election is
definitive and I will participate to win,” said Rezai, a former
commander of the Revolutionary Guards, according to ILNA.  Rezai, who ran in the 2009 race and lost to President
 Mahmoud Ahmadinejad , spoke in a meeting with a group of Tehran
residents, ILNA said.  Iranian authorities haven’t yet set a date for the race.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ladane Nasseri in Dubai at 
